 Relationship heartbreak. Photo/The Law Of Attraction  The truth is that you are the only one who can make yourself happy and at times, inferiority complex could be the cause. Search yourself get, find out what you love doing and engage yourself in it for now avoid an intimate relationship or any sort of commitment, mix up with people on platonic ground and rediscover yourself. I am sure with these few tips, if followed effectively, you would know who you really are and what you really want in any kind of relationship with people and you would realise before anyone can make you happy, you have to be happy and confident with yourself. This is just a friendly suggestion. Thanks. -Ify Advice: Dear readers, mail your comments, reactions or true love stories, quiz or personal experience you wish to share to: simonclar@yahoo.com To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .